8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;WP4ME: Valentina Olini, Web Designer Freelance, ci racconterà la sua esperienza&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/295971799/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Blocks:verso il Full Site Editing e oltre!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/295262049/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 21 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;La mia cassetta per gli attrezzi: plugin e tool&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/295779110/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 22 set, ore 18:00 &#8220;Perché utilizzare un sito di staging&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/295718967/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vicenza</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 26 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Ask Me Anything&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-vicenza/events/295924612/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";