le community di: [&#8230;]\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"Margherita Pelonara\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3250:\"\n<p>In tutta Italia ci sono meetup WordPress!</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I meetup sono <strong>incontri gratuiti e aperti a tutti,</strong>&nbsp;in cui le community locali si incontrano per condividere conoscenze, conoscersi e fare rete.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-3605\"></span>\n\n\n\n<p>Se non sai cos’è un meetup&nbsp;<a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/guida-ai-meetup-di-wordpress/\">leggi qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tutti i meetup WordPress italiani attivi sono&nbsp;<a href=\"https://it.wordpress.org/meetup/\">elencati qui.</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Nei prossimi giorni, <em>in ordine cronologico</em>, si incontrano le community di:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Milano</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 13 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;WordPress come strumento di empowerment per giovani attivisti&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-milano/events/295043036/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Verona</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>lun 18 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Multipagina, one page o landing page?&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/294758493\">iscriviti qui per </a><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/verona-wordpress-meetup/events/295885114/\">p</a><a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/treviso-wordpress-meetup/events/294758493\">artecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Pisa</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 19 set, ore 18:00 &#8220;WordPress e l&#8217;utilizzo dell&#8217;editor a blocchi (Gutenberg)&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/pisa-wordpress-meetup/events/295173372/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Genova</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;WP4ME: Valentina Olini, Web Designer Freelance, ci racconterà la sua esperienza&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-genova/events/295971799/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Napoli</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mer 20 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Blocks:verso il Full Site Editing e oltre!&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-napoli-meetup/events/295262049/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Torino</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>gio 21 set, ore 18:30 &#8220;La mia cassetta per gli attrezzi: plugin e tool&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-torino/events/295779110/\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Roma</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>ven 22 set, ore 18:00 &#8220;Perché utilizzare un sito di staging&#8221; &#8211; <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/romawordpress/events/295718967/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Vicenza</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>mar 26 set, ore 19:00 &#8220;Ask Me Anything&#8221; &#8211; <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.meetup.com/it-IT/wordpress-meetup-vicenza/events/295924612/\" target=\"_blank\">iscriviti qui per partecipare</a></p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http